Module FinalProject
Package provided.pubsubsync

Interface IPubSubSyncChannelWatchOnly

All Known Subinterfaces:
IPubSubSyncChannelUpdate<T>
public interface IPubSubSyncChannelWatchOnly
Represents a Watch Only listener connection on a pubsub channel. The channel cannot be updated through this listener. Data syncs from the pubsub sync server are received however.
Author:
Stephen Wong (c) 2020
